cs.IT, cs.SI, cs.NI, cs.MM, cs.LG. 

This paper deals with information theory and communication systems, which are typically categorized under cs.IT. The use of variable-length feedback and the analysis of asymptotic behavior suggest that the paper may also fall under cs.SI (signal processing), cs.NI (networking and internet architecture), and cs.MM (multimedia). The use of renewal theory suggests a possible categorization under cs.LG (machine learning).
